selected me as a sacrifice.

28
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,240
You do bear some

29
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,000
resemblance to Mo Xiuxiu.

30
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,480
[But Xiu]

31
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,560
is not Mo Xiuxiu after all.

32
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,120
Halt!

33
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,880
Stay where you are!

34
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,320
Jing Lin, stay alert.

35
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,200
What is the meaning of this?

36
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,600
Release Lord Mo, now!

37
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,040
He's conspired with the Fire Moth Sect,

38
