Lord Mo is a guardian of the people,

42
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,360
[fighting valiantly against the spectres.]

43
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,480
[When the criminal Ji Dafu was executed,]

44
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,760
Lord Shen intervened multiple times,

45
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:15,240
clearly with ulterior motives.

46
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,800
Lord Mo instructed us

47
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,840
to remain vigilant.

48
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,000
And indeed,

49
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:20,560
we uncovered that you

50
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,360
[were secretly colluding with the spectres.]

51
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:22,920
[Now,]

52
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,400
[you're caught abducting Lord Mo]

53
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,320
[and turn the tables on us?]

54
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,400
You are framing us!

55
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:29,360
Since Lord Shen's arrival,

56
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:31,360
[the masked spectres have emerged]

57
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,480
[like mushrooms after a rainstorm.]

58
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,560
Is this merely a coincidence?

59
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:35,960
[This is utterly foolish.]

60
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:36,960
You have all been

61
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,400
deceived by Mo Qianzhi's facade!

62
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,320
Exactly who abducted you all?

63
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:41,960
Xiu,

64
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,520
you must reveal the truth.

65
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:45,480
Mo is the one colluding with the spectres,

66
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,120
planning to use you

67
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,120
as sacrifices.

68
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,000
Shen Du,

69
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,840
[we haven't met in years.]

70
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:58,680
[I never imagined you'd]

71
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,640
[end up to be such a corrupted official.]

72
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,960
Surrender yourselves!

73
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,960
Corrupt officials!

74
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,080
Release Lord Mo at once!

75
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,880
Mo Qianzhi is the true culprit behind the

76
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,760
masked spectres' atrocities in the city.

77
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,320
He has exploited

78
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,640
the trust of all of you!

79
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,440
The White Death!

80
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,680
Release Lord Mo immediately!

81
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,560
[Lord Mo is a compassionate official]

82
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,960
[who genuinely cares for the people!]

83
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,920
[He is always concerned about us.]

84
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,600
Don't you frame him!

85
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:21,000
Release Lord Mo!

86
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,520
What are you trying to do?

87
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,040
Step back! Back!

88
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,520
Don't harm the civilians!

89
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,640
Neither violence nor reasoning

90
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,000
will resolve this situation.

91
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,160
[These people]

92
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,120
[have lost their minds!]

93
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,920
Shen Du,

94
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,680
[guise or genuine,]

95
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,000
[they've figured it out,]

96
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,040
have you?

97
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,440
So this is your true scheme.

98
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,760
Hold on!

99
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,160
Stop!

100
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,080
Sun Tan!

101
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,360
Are you delinquents revolting?

102
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,800
Apologies, Lord Mo.

103
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,440
You all know

104
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,520
how difficult we are to deal with!

105
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,400
Everyone, step back! Step back!

106
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,760
Let them go!

107
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,160
Come on. Move!

108
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:47,120
We're grateful for your aid earlier.

109
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,160
Lord Shen, I'm truly humbled.

110
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,800
Chief has sent a letter instructing me

111
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,360
to assist Lady Yan with the investigation.

112
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,080
This is indeed our duty.

113
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:56,320
If it weren't for your aid earlier,

114
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,320
the citizens in the city

115
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,560
would have surely

116
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,320
drowned us with their spittle.

117
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,880
To the people of Yingzhou,

118
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,200
Lord Mo is a

119
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,400
rare and exemplary official.

120
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,800
In disasters, he opens soup kitchens,

121
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,480
offering free porridge to those in need.

122
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,240
On normal days, he leads the constables

123
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,680
to repair houses for the citizens

124
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,200
[without any charge.]

125
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,760
[With his exceptional behavior,]

126
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,920
[how could the people]

127
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,000
ever perceive him as a villain?

128
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,720
On one hand, he's cherished by the people,

129
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,240
and respected by his peers as a virtuous man,

130
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,360
while on the other, he is a madman who

131
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,200
disregards life and follows a cult.

132
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,680
It's hard to see through

133
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,560
these two personas.

134
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,760
For now, we can only stay outside the city

135
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,600
and observe how things unfold.

136
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,320
I truly appreciate

137
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,720
the delinquents, our brothers-in-arms,

138
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,280
who have stood by us in this situation.

139
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,920
I, the head of the Delinquents

140
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,760
in Gannan,

141
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:43,920
place my trust in those

142
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,920
acknowledged by our chief.

143
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,360
Lord Shen,

144
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,880
we've just received a classified message

145
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,000
from Xiang'an.

146
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,720
Her Majesty has issued a decree to mobilize

147
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,320
the troops of the neighboring counties.

148
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,520
She orders me and General Zhenyuan

149
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,520
to capture Mo Qianzhi alive.

150
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,840
But Mo Qianzhi just drove us

151
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,880
out of the city.

152
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,400
The message came with unexpected haste!

153
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,320
Prior to our arrival,

154
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,400
Her Majesty summoned me and

155
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,160
[ordered me to keep an eye on Mo Qianzhi.]

156
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,080
Upon my arrival in Yingzhou,

157
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:23,080
an agent reached me through covert means.

158
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,200
That must be Biqiu

159
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,280
who was murdered not long ago.

160
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,400
It's very likely that Mo

161
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,840
sensed something amiss and reported

162
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,440
the news to Xiang'an early this morning.

163
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,200
So it appears,

164
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,560
the entire world,

165
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,640
inside and outside the imperial realm,

166
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:37,600
is under Her Majesty's

167
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,080
watchful eye.

168
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,000
Based on this, it is evident

169
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,560
that sending me to Gannan region

170
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:44,840
to handle the case of the masked spectre

171
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,760
was also part of Her Majesty's

172
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,600
calculations.

173
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,600
Her Majesty

174
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,960
has ordered you to seize Yingzhou.

175
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,080
If a war breaks out,

176
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,760
what will happen to the citizens within?

177
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,840
I pray for a turn in our fortunes

178
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,560
before General Zhenyuan's arrival.

179
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,520
Who is it?

180
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,200
Who is it?

181
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,200
Show yourself!

182
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,360
Qi Yeyun?

183
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,560
Sneaking around,

184
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,080
you want us to catch you or something?

185
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,720
Sis taught me to act this way.

186
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,520
Always observe carefully first,

187
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,080
Caution ensures lasting safety!

188
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,400
[I, Shen Du, am here.]

189
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,400
[I need to have a word with Mo Qianzhi!]

190
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,320
If you want to talk,

191
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,640
come up and talk!

192
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,320
You really dare to come alone,

193
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,560
aren't you afraid I could end you?

194
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,920
I'm here to deliver

195
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,080
the ultimatum.

196
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,320
Xiang'an's aware of your suspicious activities.

197
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,960
Her Majesty has dispatched troops

198
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,960
to Yingzhou.

199
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,360
It's not too late to back down now.

200
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,520
They planned to launch an attack?

201
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,800
It won't be as simple

202
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,680
as they think.

203
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,120
You believe that the

204
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,200
tens of thousands of citizens in the city,

205
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,080
along with those few masked spectres,

206
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,320
are enough to challenge

207
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,200
the imperial army?

208
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,040
The will of the masses

209
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,800
can stand against legions.

210
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,480
Do you recall the vow you made

211
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,320
when you became my father's disciple?

212
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,120
To serve the empire with loyalty

213
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,440
without disappointing the populace.

214
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:38,920
Shen Du,

215
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,160
I honestly never imagined

216
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:43,040
that one day you would say this to me.

217
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,560
Can't you see

218
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:47,720
that the current empire

219
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:49,440
is already infested with corruption?

220
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,640
Its downfall is just a matter of time.

221
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,320
Then eliminate these corrupt elements

222
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,320
instead of toppling the entire empire.

223
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,200
The Fire Moth Sect

224
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,520
has always been ruthless,

225
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,960
ready to betray anyone at any moment.

226
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,280
Are you really willing to gamble

227
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:13,040
with the lives of

228
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,240
these innocent citizens?

229
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:24,600
If you want to negotiate,

230
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,720
I'm open to it,

231
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,600
but you must agree to one condition.

232
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,160
What condition?

233
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,560
Bring me

234
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,880
the head of Lady Yan.

235
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,240
Then there's nothing to discuss.

236
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,680
My dear Du,

237
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,240
she is the Queen's pawn,

238
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,200
[a mere tool used by her]

239
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,800
[to manipulate you!]

240
00:12:59,160 --> 00:12:59,960
Without her,

241
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,800
you will finally see clearly

242
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,480
the true state of devastation

243
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,280
that has befallen the empire!

244
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,920
The one blinded by hatred

245
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,680
is you.

246
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,040
This time,

247
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:13,240
you've truly made a mistake.

248
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,080
I made a mistake?

249
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,640
You're treating your foe like a father.

250
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:34,840
No,

251
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:36,320
like a mother, I suppose.

252
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:41,040
What she consumes daily

253
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:43,120
is the delicacies stained with

254
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,280
the blood of your kin!

255
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,520
[What she revels in]

256
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,960
is the wealth and luxury built upon

257
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,080
the bones of your kin!

258
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:52,480
I made a mistake?

259
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,560
Aren't you even more absurdly wrong!

260
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,160
Don't you yearn to uncover the truth?

261
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,160
This is a sack used for storing supplies.

262
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,720
Why does it bear the mark

263
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,800
of the granary from back then,

264
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:17,480
and why is it found

265
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:19,160
in Gannan, a thousand miles away?

266
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,400
Shouldn't these

267
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,440
have been destroyed

268
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,960
in the fire back then?

269
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,080
Have you ever considered

270
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,360
that my master,

271
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:30,080
your father

272
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:31,600
was actually guarding

273
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,480
a treasury

274
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,080
that had already been emptied!

275
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:42,120
I will uncover the truth myself.

276
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:45,520
But you want to gamble

277
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:47,360
the lives of all the citizens in this city

278
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:49,040
and risk a massacre

279
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,600
to secure your own future.

280
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:53,160
I'm afraid I must disagree!

281
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,240
Just stop.

282
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,360
I have very few

283
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,840
loved ones left in this world.

284
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,960
I don't need your approval.

285
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,320
There's no turning back now.

286
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:34,360
I have planned and endured for so long,

287
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,720
