Why are you so impulsive?

579
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,000
Du!

580
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:57,440
Have everyone else step back.

581
00:36:59,080 --> 00:36:59,880
Come here,

582
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:01,840
I need to talk to you.

583
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:24,840
Du,

584
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:28,600
I knew you got out of the Custodial Ward,

585
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,560
[and I've heard you've become]

586
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:31,760
[the commander of the Imperial Guard.]

587
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:34,040
[I've also heard you've become]

588
00:37:34,200 --> 00:37:35,280
[cold-hearted and ruthless.]

589
00:37:36,040 --> 00:37:37,840
But I'm genuinely happy for you.

590
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:42,080
You're the last survivor of the Shens.

591
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:44,720
If you were still gentle and naive,

592
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:46,920
how could you possibly avenge master

593
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,840
and the rest of the Shen Family?

594
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,480
After establishing the Imperial Guard,

595
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,360
I have been diligently investigating.

596
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,120
On the surface,

597
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:58,680
the evidence in the Shens' case

598
00:37:58,680 --> 00:37:59,600
appears irrefutable.

599
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,760
Yet I still uncovered

600
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:01,680
some suspicious details.

601
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:04,240
The events could not possibly have been

602
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:08,200
orchestrated by a single person.

603
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,960
Master was inherently modest,

604
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:16,160
always seeking to avoid court intrigues.

605
00:38:16,680 --> 00:38:18,480
[His only concern was for the people.]

606
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:20,520
Regardless of who it was in power,

607
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:22,400
he simply did what he believed was right.

608
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:24,840
Peace for the people was his only wish.

609
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,320
[His very wish]

610
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:29,480
[offended the interests of many.]

611
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:30,520
The Majesty,

612
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:31,720
to whom you are devoted,

613
00:38:32,240 --> 00:38:33,880
desired nothing less than his submission.

614
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:35,720
The ones responsible for the Shens' demise

615
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,160
were the Zhou Family.

616
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,000
I will definitely get to the bottom

617
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,440
of what happened back then.

618
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:45,200
No matter how many years it takes,

619
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:46,560
no matter who I will cross,

620
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:48,840
I will seek justice

621
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:50,280
from them one by one.

622
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:52,840
To bring peace to the souls

623
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,640
of the dozens who died unjustly.

624
00:38:59,080 --> 00:38:59,880
Du,

625
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,480
I never thought

626
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:04,120
that you and I would find ourselves

627
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:06,000
at odds due to the same hatred.

628
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,960
Should you ever have your revenge,

629
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:09,640
remember to light an incense in my memory.

630
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,240
When I journey to the afterlife,

631
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,680
I will finally find peace...

632
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:15,840
Qianzhi!

633
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:17,480
[Qianzhi!]

634
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:25,840
I left something

635
00:39:27,040 --> 00:39:28,440
for you in

636
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:30,680
Xiu's portrait.

637
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,080
Qianzhi...

638
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,000
Gosh!

639
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,840
Retribution has arrived!

640
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,680
Right after Lord Mo's departure,

641
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:09,120
this bizarre incident occurred.

642
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:10,440
This is divine retribution!

643
00:41:18,160 --> 00:41:18,960
It's poisoning.

644
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:20,640
Move aside!

645
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,600
Lord Shen,

646
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:27,520
there have been several reports

647
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,920
of this strange phenomenon in the city.

648
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:30,400
It's truly alarming.

649
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,520
Over thirty citizens have been affected.

650
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,560
If this continues,

651
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,960
we're bound to face chaos.

652
00:41:36,080 --> 00:41:37,360
This is the work of the Fire Moth Sect.

653
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,280
[If we can't find a solution...]

654
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:39,960
Then

655
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,720
the Fire Moth Sect could use this poison

656
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,200
to take down the entire city

657
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:45,120
without a single drop of bloodshed.

658
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,600
Although this poison is potent,

659
00:41:50,080 --> 00:41:51,400
its effects are slow to manifest.

660
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:52,280
For now,

661
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,320
they are not in immediate danger.

662
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:55,640
I will find a way

663
00:41:55,640 --> 00:41:56,640
to obtain the antidote.

664
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:57,280
Understood!

665
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,200
You take over.

666
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:00,280
Understood!

667
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:13,240
[I left something]

668
00:42:13,720 --> 00:42:16,800
[for you in Xiu's portrait.]

